Gayle Hunnicutt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gayle_Hunnicutt 0 Gayle Hunnicutt, Lady Jenkins, (born February 6, 1943), is an American film, television and stage actress, based in the United Kingdom for many years. She has made more than 30 film appearances.
